column5: On the water early this morning. Lots of herring jumping around and smelts as well were in the mix.  Didnt take long to get a couple for dinner tonight. Went 2 for 4. Love it when a plan comes together.
oh black and whitie pictures lol
Nice shooting!  How ya gonna cook em up?

Nice shooting!  How ya gonna cook em up?   I cooked them up just like this,,,,,,,,,,,, Fish Crisp  My youngest son has worked all weekend and we have been watching his little girl. This will be a great surprise for him when he gets in.  Oh I kept a few pieces for meself.
Nice!  I gotta try em fried. I always bake or bbq mine
Great job, enjoy the feast.  You made me drool a little with that last pic.
Mmmmmm fish crisp...... My mouth is watering!  Nice indeed!
Nice catching and some exercise to boot,congrats
